The paper deals with the linear inverse problem, which is a common topic in information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.SP). The focus is on convex programs, which are widely used in machine learning and optimization (cs.LG). The paper also introduces a new set and cone, which are relevant to numerical analysis (cs.NA) and optimization (cs.SI).
